&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Without Questions in life what is the need for a Guru? &lt;br>
If my questions are well defined then do I need a Guru? &lt;br>
Guru helps in defining questions well &lt;br>
or answering whatever you ask? &lt;br>
Does he empower you by giving more information &lt;br>
or make you restless by holding half answer?&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>